    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Inserting material into a hole, crack, or cavity. In the specific context of mosaic conservation, the application of mortar or other material into an area of loss of the mosaic surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
